following listed directions, it may be easier to download a pre-compiled binary. Make sure to verify and get the latest version.

For example, to get the v.0.22.2 version, do:

$ curl -Lo minikube https://storage.googleapis.com/minikube/releases/latest/minikube-darwin-amd64

$ chmod +x minikube

$ sudo mv minikube /usr/local/bin


NOTE
A good Github to follow and read to know more about Minikube - https://github.com/kubernetes/minikube
